# Codebook for Clean Dataset

## Variables

- month  
  Format YYYY-MM. Represents each month in the dataset.

- petrol_price  
  Monthly average petrol price in AUD per litre.  
  Source: FuelIO (manually extracted).

- patronage_total  
  Total monthly public transport usage (train + tram + bus).  
  Source: Transport Patronage | vic.gov.au.

## Notes
- All dates converted to YYYY-MM format.
- Missing values checked and handled during cleaning.
- Dataset is ready for regression analysis.